{"tid":2179235,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鯉魚門魔鬼山有綠寶石礦","createTime":"2020-08-29T03:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T04:34:25.000Z","uid":261647,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"69cefef3509cce64761050bbe49059b1f7c4939c","tid":2179235,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T03:17:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/465275270191417/photos/a.673369946048614/3447492308636350/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F465275270191417%2Fphotos%2Fa.673369946048614%2F3447492308636350%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5Zp1eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=50a7f0dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/465275270191417/photos/a.673369946048614/3447492308636350/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pNQj4G0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpNQj4G0.jpg&h=b3395da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋寶夢（一）：鯉魚門魔鬼山（ Devil's Peak）附近村民叫鬼仔山。1955年9月，一位退役英軍上魔鬼山一段路豎立了多少個「私人重地，非請勿進，送官究治」的告示牌，並搭建了多個軍用帳幕。魔鬼山是昔日軍事禁地，建有堡壘和炮台，戰後已荒廢，設施毀壞，人跡杳然。這位退役英軍名為哈里斯，何故要在魔鬼山豎立告示牌和搭建帳幕？皆因他在山上挖掘出綠柱石礦，即綠寶石礦，他在舊日軍區房屋設立採礦辦公室，並聘用工人展開探礦工程，工人就在帳幕留宿。消息傳出，市民議論紛紛，說他掘到寶，成為「千萬富翁」。"},{"pid":"b6260ea0f2c6f3074b72b94713d9923f3cda640a","tid":2179235,"uid":49163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:11:56.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n上次行山都執到粒"},{"pid":"c3d9ce75274207b04d1ba24e2bb715fde2572a03","tid":2179235,"uid":321374,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:32:21.000Z","msg":"鑽石山有山咁大粒既鑽石<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efcdfa4f16aa96b1f05062d0fd1e40f629cfcbd","tid":2179235,"uid":276865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b6260ea0f2c6f3074b72b94713d9923f3cda640a","tid":2179235,"uid":49163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:11:56.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n上次行山都執到粒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-